{{main|諾瓦克·喬科維奇}}
'''諾瓦克·喬科維奇2011年賽季'''，是被網球界認為男子網球最成功和影響力最大的一個賽季之一<ref name="NYTimesintro">{{cite web|url=http://www.tennis.com.au/news/2011/11/20/djokovic-plays-down-fitness-worries|title=Djokovic plays down fitness worries|work=tennis.com.au|date=2011-11-20|publisher=Tennis Australia|accessdate=2012-03-05|archive-date=2013-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131230233958/http://www.tennis.com.au/news/2011/11/20/djokovic-plays-down-fitness-worries|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該賽季，喬科維奇對戰兩大球員[[費德勒|費德勒]]和[[拉斐爾·納達爾|納達爾]]取得10勝1負的戰績，其中對納達爾取得決賽6連勝的成績，包含兩個大滿貫冠軍。喬科維奇從年初的[[2011年澳洲網球公開賽|澳洲網球公開賽]]一直連勝到[[2011年法國網球公開賽|法國公開賽]]四強，取得一波41連勝的高潮。他全年11次闖進決賽，拿到10個冠軍，包括3個大滿貫和5個大師賽冠軍<ref name="NYTimesintro" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.atpworldtour.com/News/Tennis/2011/08/32/Montreal-Final-Djokovic-Wins-Fifth-Masters-1000.aspx|title=Djokovic Makes Masters 1000 History In Montreal|author=ATP Staff|date=2011-08-14|publisher=ATP World Tour|accessdate=2011-11-14|archive-date=2013-06-21|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6HWz8SKrg?url=http://www.atpworldtour.com/News/Tennis/2011/08/32/Montreal-Final-Djokovic-Wins-Fifth-Masters-1000.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>，全年取得70勝6負的戰績，並在7月贏得溫網之後，取代納達爾成為新的世界第一，也是自2004年以來，第三位登上男子單打世界第一的網球員<ref name="YEN1">{{cite web|url=http://www.atpworldtour.com/News/Tennis/2011/10/Features/Djokovic-Clinches-Year-End-No-1-Ranking.aspx|title=Djokovic Clinches Year-End No. 1 For First Time|date=2011-10-13|accessdate=2014-07-20|work=Association of Tennis Professionals|archive-date=2014-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141112160214/http://www.atpworldtour.com/News/Tennis/2011/10/Features/Djokovic-Clinches-Year-End-No-1-Ranking.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。全年破紀錄拿到 1260萬美元的獎金<ref name="賽程和獎金">{{cite web|url=http://www.atpworldtour.com/Tennis/Players/Top-Players/Novak-Djokovic.aspx?t=pa&y=2011&m=s&e=0#|title=2011 Singles Activity|work=ATP World Tour|date=|publisher=|accessdate=2015-04-11|archive-date=2015-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150325161603/http://www.atpworldtour.com/Tennis/Players/Top-Players/Novak-Djokovic.aspx?t=pa&y=2011&m=s&e=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。因為該賽季的出色表現，喬科維奇被網球界和媒體界授予多個獎項，其中包括2012年年初頒發的最著名的[[勞倫斯世界體育獎|勞倫斯世界體育獎最佳男運動員獎]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.laureus.com/news/laureus-world-sportsman-year-novak-djokovic|title=Laureus World Sportsman of the Year - Novak Djokovic|author=|date=|publisher=Laureus official website|accessdate=2015-04-16|archive-date=2014-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141219164943/http://www.laureus.com/news/laureus-world-sportsman-year-novak-djokovic|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 全年概覽 ==
=== 季初硬地賽 ===
{{main article|2011年澳洲網球公開賽}}
[[File:Novak_Djokovic_at_the_2011_Australian_Open4.jpg|thumb]]

喬科維奇沒有參加熱身賽直接參加澳網，於四強的比賽中直落三盤擊敗賽會四屆冠軍得主費德勒，第二度闖入澳網決賽<ref name="AUSSFONE">{{cite web|url=http://www.heraldsun.com.au/sport/australian-open-2011/novak-djokovic-upsets-roger-federer-in-australian-open-semi-final/story-fn77kxzt-1225995803984|title=Novak Djokovic upsets Roger Federer in Australian Open semi-final|last=Schlink|first=Leo|date=2011-01-28|publisher=The Herald and Weekly Times|accessdate=2011-09-30|archive-date=2020-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725183103/https://www.heraldsun.com.au/archive/old-sport-pages/novak-djokovic-upsets-roger-federer-in-australian-open-semi-final/news-story/ee77d7c36872fe470d523fde60d2d57f?nk=38696b75c0b8561efb7e7834ee95584f-1595701863|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隨後喬科維奇在決賽遭遇[[穆雷|穆雷]]，並以直落三盤的比分擊敗穆雷，贏得職業生涯第二座澳網冠軍<ref name=AOFINAL>{{cite web|url=http://www.heraldsun.com.au/ipad/djokovic-wins-in-straight-sets/story-fn6bn7je-1225997095404|title=Novak Djokovic wins in straight sets|publisher=The Herald and Weekly Times|work=heraldsun.com.au|last=Schlink|first=Leo|date=2011-01-30|accessdate=2011-09-30|archive-date=2020-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725183105/https://www.heraldsun.com.au/ipad/djokovic-wins-in-straight-sets/news-story/23c87807702c319e5cf3d3831d3784fb?nk=f57d6a47290dfb86b3a84de59296ae46-1595701865|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

二月份喬科維奇轉戰中東賽季，在杜拜錦標賽決賽再次擊敗費德勒，獲得第三個杜拜賽的冠軍<ref name=DUBAIFL>{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/tennis/9408376.stm|title=Novak Djokovic defeats Roger Federer to win Dubai title|date=2011-02-26|work=BBC Sport|publisher=BBC|accessdate=2011-09-30|archive-date=2011-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110531215424/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/tennis/9408376.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 北美硬地賽 ===
{{main article|2011年印第安維爾斯大師賽|2011年邁阿密大師賽}}
喬科維奇於北美硬地賽中表現突出。在印第安維爾斯大師賽準決賽淘汰費德勒，也是該年度第三次擊敗後者，闖入決賽的喬科維奇面對前賽會冠軍和世界第一納達爾，喬科維奇在先輸一盤的情況下逆轉賽果贏得冠軍，而喬科維奇也確定上升至世界第二<ref name=IWSF>{{cite web|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/sports/tennis/news/story?id=6237014|title=Roger Federer out at Indian Wells|agency=Associated Press|date=2011-03-20|publisher=ESPN|accessdate=2011-09-30|archive-date=2011-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110511162240/http://sports.espn.go.com/sports/tennis/news/story?id=6237014|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=IWFL>{{cite web|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2011/mar/20/sports/la-sp-dwyre-20110321|title=Novak Djokovic finds a secret to tennis success and a dent in Rafael Nadal's armor|last=Dwyre|first=Bill|date=2011-03-20|work=Los Angeles Times|accessdate=2011-09-30|archive-date=2011-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110406210405/http://articles.latimes.com/2011/mar/20/sports/la-sp-dwyre-20110321|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在邁阿密大師賽決賽中，喬科維奇於該年度第二次與納達爾交手，結果與印第安維爾斯一樣，喬科維奇在先輸一盤的情況再次逆轉比賽，贏得邁阿密大師賽的冠軍，也是繼費德勒之後，第二位背靠背贏得春季北美兩個大師賽冠軍的球員<ref name=Miami>{{cite web|url=http://news.scotsman.com/tennis/Novak-Djokovic-hot-streak-rolls.6745460.jp|title=Novak Djokovic hot streak rolls on as Rafael Nadal is edged out|last=Fodens|first=Eve|date=2011-04-04|work=The Scotsman|location=UK|accessdate=2011-09-30|archive-date=2020-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200723051807/https://www.scotsman.com/news|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 紅土賽季 ===
喬科維奇於家鄉[[貝爾格萊德|貝爾格萊德]]參加塞爾維亞公開賽，最終贏得年度第五個冠軍，直到本站賽事為止，喬科維奇已經取得了賽季27連勝<ref name="IndExpintro">{{cite web|url=http://www.indianexpress.com/news/djokovic-extends-streak-to-27-with-serbia-op/784348/|title=Djokovic extends streak to 27 with Serbia Open title|agency=Reuters|work=The Indian Express|location=New Delhi, India|date=2011-05-02|publisher=Indian Express Limited|accessdate=2011-10-17|archive-date=2020-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725183053/http://archive.indianexpress.com/news/djokovic-extends-streak-to-27-with-serbia-op/784348|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

{{main article|2011年馬德里大師賽|2011年羅馬大師賽}}
喬科維奇因為膝傷退出了蒙特卡洛大師賽，但之後回到賽場參加馬德里大師賽，在決賽中第三次與納達爾交手，在開場4比0領先的情況下，被納達爾連贏5局，但喬科維奇在盤末取得關鍵破發以7-5贏得首盤，最終以直落兩盤的比分首次在[[紅土球場|紅土場]]擊敗納達爾，贏得職業生涯第一座馬德里賽冠軍<ref name=MadridFL>{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/tennis/13328382.stm|title=Novak Djokovic ends Nadal's run on clay in Madrid|last=Newbery|first=Piers|date=2011-05-08|work=BBC Sports|accessdate=2011-09-30|archive-date=2011-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110531190306/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/tennis/13328382.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

