== 外界評價 ==
《[[TENNIS_Magazine|網球雜誌]]》將喬科維奇這一賽季評為網球公開化年代以來，第三個最偉大的賽季，排在費德勒[[2006年羅傑·費德勒網球賽季|2006年賽季]]和[[羅德·拉沃|羅德·拉沃]]的1969年賽季之後<ref name="3rdseason">{{cite web|author=張奔斗|work=[[體壇周報|體壇周報]]|title=德约科维奇缔造史上最强赛季 网坛沦落至最坏年代|url=http://sports.titan24.com/tennis/2011-12-20/187983.html#p=1|publisher=|location=|date=2011-12-20|accessdate=2015-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150417042711/http://sports.titan24.com/tennis/2011-12-20/187983.html#p=1|archive-date=2015-04-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。[[皮特·桑普拉斯|桑普拉斯]]甚至將其形容為“所有體育運動中最優秀的其中一個成就”<ref>[http://www.palmbeachpost.com/news/sports/after-putting-on-couch-potato-weight-in-retireme-1/nLyDk/  Hal Habib (21 September 2011). "After putting on 'couch potato' weight in retirement, Pete Sampras is fit again and playing competitively".] {{Wayback|url=http://www.palmbeachpost.com/news/sports/after-putting-on-couch-potato-weight-in-retireme-1/nLyDk/ |date=20140221232013 }} The Palm Beach Post.[2015-04-11]</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://novakdjokovic.com/en/news/media/pete-sampras-novaks-season-best-ive-seen-in-my-lifetime/|title=Pete Sampras: Novak’s season best I’ve seen in my lifetime|date=2011-09-25|accessdate=2015-04-16|publisher=Novak Djokovic officlal website|archive-date=2015-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150426125129/http://novakdjokovic.com/en/news/media/pete-sampras-novaks-season-best-ive-seen-in-my-lifetime/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之前幾個賽季被納達爾壓著的喬科維奇，2011年賽季打出了對對手的六連勝。喬科維奇不僅在硬地上取得對納達爾的連勝，而在納達爾最為擅長的紅土上喬科維奇也取得了對後者的二連勝，且所有比賽都發生在決賽。而納達爾談到對喬科維奇的連敗，納達爾表示喬科維奇這一年的表現是他職業生涯以來見過的最好的表現<ref>{{cite web|url=http://uk.eurosport.yahoo.com/19112011/2/tennis-nadal-returns-unfamiliar-role-underdog.html|title=Nadal returns in unfamiliar role of underdog|date=2011-11-19|accessdate=2014-07-19|publisher=Yahoo! News|archive-date=2013-06-24|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6HcUjXAaw?url=http://uk.eurosport.yahoo.com/19112011/2/tennis-nadal-returns-unfamiliar-role-underdog.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。現任教練[[鮑里斯·貝克|鮑里斯·貝克]]認為，這一賽季事網球史上